<view class="guide-mask" wx:if="{{show}}">
  <view class="guide-card">
    <view class="guide-header">
      <text class="title">接收血压预警</text>
    </view>
    <view class="guide-body">
      <view class="main-text">
        <text class="highlight">{{inviterName}} </text> 想在
        <text class="highlight"> {{profileName}} </text>
        血压异常时通知您。
      </view>
      <view class="instruction-box">
        <text class="inst-title">点击下方按钮弹出授权窗口后：</text>
        <text class="inst-item">• 请开启<text class="bold">【指标异常提醒】</text>开关</text>
        <text class="inst-item">• 再点击<text class="bold">【允许】</text>按钮</text>
        <text class="inst-item">• 并勾选<text class="bold">【总是保持以上选择】</text></text>
      </view>
      <view class="warning-text">
        ※ 如果点击拒绝，将无法收到血压异常提醒
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="guide-footer">
      <button class="guide-btn-primary" bindtap="onSubscribe">开启通知</button>
      <button class="guide-btn-secondary" bindtap="onReject">暂不</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
